title: Find a sustainable wood fuel supplier

heading_context: Find a sustainable wood fuel supplier
chunks.html_content: Find a registered supplier of biomass wood fuel that meets the Renewable Heat Incentive (RHI) requirements.
chunks.plain_content:
Find a sustainable wood fuel supplier
Find a registered supplier of biomass wood fuel that meets the Renewable Heat Incentive (RHI) requirements.

heading_context: Find a sustainable wood fuel supplier
chunks.html_content: The suppliers on this list meet the requirements for both of the RHI schemes: domestic and non-domestic.
chunks.plain_content:
Find a sustainable wood fuel supplier
The suppliers on this list meet the requirements for both of the RHI schemes: domestic and non-domestic.

heading_context: Find a sustainable wood fuel supplier
chunks.html_content:
Use this service if you:

  • have a biomass boiler or are thinking of getting one
  • use wood fuel
  • have already joined the domestic or non-domestic RHI scheme, or are thinking of joining either
